<p>袁程程讲述单玉厚感人事迹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201015/6a9624b05c844527963ffd633917626f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
